AUDIO: 'us don\'t believe so because this this time is truly different in that um there\'s no ne there\'s not necessarily any reason for any of the new jobs to be done by humans. Um so if wages fall from 60 to 80% of aggregate demand to 20 to'

[04:59] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: '50% that\'s a fundamentally different paradigm that we\'re going to be entering into. At the same time again you don\'t want to punish uh wages when you measure it. Um, but you really want to put the lion share of of of priority into'

[05:12] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
