VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'share. even if the government is helped managing it, if it\'s not paid for directly by taxes, then it\'s property or wage. So the formula, and by the way, this is a proposed formula. This hasn\'t been finalized. We actually need to get'

[05:50] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'the data together and build the dashboard and and and do some experimentation, but property plus beta times wages minus transfers. And then scale uh so then this is then rescaled. So it\'ll be on a score of uh 0 to 100.'

