AUDIO: 'right, next slide. One thing that comes up is some people ask me like, you know, oh well Dave, why don\'t we just do UBI? And I\'ve I\'ve heard everyone from the effective altruist talking about UBI only uh or universal basic dividends or'

[12:18] [scene:talk]
