AUDIO: 'power. Next up is the concept of align incentives. Broader ownership streams synchronize the interests of finance firms and local governments around a single goal, resilient demand. Again, aggregate demand is what everyone wants. And if aggregate demand is based mostly'

[21:59] [scene:talk]
